<template>

  export default {
    props:['mini'],
    data () {
      return {
        drawer: false,
        items: [

          { title: 'App', icon: 'mdi-apps',route:'/teams' },
          { title: 'Projects', icon: 'mdi-folder-multiple',route:'/teams' },
         
        ],

    },
  }
</script>
